<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
  <h1 class="h3 mb-0"><i class="bi bi-toggles2 text-primary me-2"></i>Configurações de Campo (check-in)</h1>
</div>

<div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
  <div class="card-body">
    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">
      <i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill text-success me-2"></i>Feature check-in geolocalizado
    </h5>

    <p class="text-muted small">
      Quando <strong>ativada</strong>, o PWA <code>/field</code> aceita login dos corretores e as rotas <code>/field/*</code> respondem normalmente.
      Quando <strong>desativada</strong>, todas as rotas <code>/field/*</code> retornam 404 e o filtro de check-in
      em <code>/admin/distribution_rules</code> fica inoperante (regras funcionam como antes).
    </p>

    <%= form_with url: admin_field_settings_path, method: :patch, local: true do |f| %>
      <div class="form-check form-switch fs-5 mb-4">
        <%= check_box_tag :enabled, "1", @enabled, class: "form-check-input", id: "field_enabled" %>
        <%= label_tag :field_enabled, "Check-in ativado", class: "form-check-label fw-bold" %>
      </div>

      <div class="d-flex justify-content-end gap-2">
        <%= link_to "Cancelar", admin_root_path, class: "btn btn-light border" %>
        <%= f.submit "Salvar", class: "btn btn-primary px-4" %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mt-3">
  <div class="card-body">
    <h6 class="fw-bold"><i class="bi bi-info-circle-fill text-info me-2"></i>Checklist antes de ativar</h6>
    <ul class="small mb-0">
      <li>Lojas cadastradas em <%= link_to "/admin/stores", admin_stores_path %> com coordenadas, raio e turnos.</li>
      <li>Corretores com <code>field_agent_enabled = true</code> + <code>default_store</code> + turnos vinculados.</li>
      <li>Worker <code>solid_queue</code> rodando com scheduler ativo (cron <code>recurring.yml</code>).</li>
      <li>PostGIS habilitado no Postgres.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
